{
  "stem": "43.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the night, everybody is going looking for bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't-- for-- for two days, I wasn't go-- I-- I didn't go out, because the older lady was with her husband, with the two children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was bleeding very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the night, what has happened-- I told, don't you-- I wouldn't let you go out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My child will bring-- we will together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so happened, I was-- I was come very oft to a Czechish couple.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was working-- the Czech-- was working in our mill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wasn't afraid that they will kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to go to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] I was, I admit-- a few days earlier, I got the last earrings what my mother-in-law gave me when I was engaged.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she gave me them-- this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, who gave everything up to the Germans-- fur, and jewelry, and everything-- copper-- whatever we got, we have to give them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The night-- she was very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I sometime, I-- I-- think maybe five wouldn't tell-- maybe she would go out-- get out!",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If she would go with me, she would-- she would be alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I-- so she so blooding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I cannot leave her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was over there when I came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When I-- when I came to the Czech, she-- oh.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She told me she will bake for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I gave her the earrings for before-- two to three days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she told me she will bake bread, and she would give me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She always gave me two bottles milk for the children and some fruit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "If she got, she gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I see them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she knows already the time when we-- when I came.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
